{"tid":300980,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎分享你最鐘意既歌詞 一齊解讀佢","createTime":"2017-06-28T10:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T10:52:14.000Z","uid":81012,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b1783991c7bc66f19e314960bbde1c96a83f5f50","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:23:31.000Z","msg":"隔離post貼左富士山下 幾鐘意大家一齊解讀作詞人用歌詞去寄情既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如一齊解下最難既呢首 不來也不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作詞：林夕   作曲：C Y Kong<br />\n揚帆時 人潮沒有你<br />\n我是我 和途人一起<br />\n停頓時 在你笑開的眼眉<br />\n望穿秋水之美<br />\n回程時 浪淘盡了你<br />\n任背影 長睡著不起<br />\n留下我 在糞土當中<br />\n翻檢背囊 直到拾回自己<br />\n<br />\n掌心因此多出一根刺<br />\n沒有刺痛便懶知<br />\n就當共你 有舊情沒有往事<br />\n<br />\n如煙 因給你遞過火<br />\n如火 卻也沒熔掉我<br />\n回望最初 當喪失是得著可不可<br />\n可痛若驪歌 樂如兒歌<br />\n像你沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<br />\n誰同行 仍同樣結尾<br />\n血液裡 才遺傳悲喜<br />\n誰亦難 避過這一身客塵<br />\n但剛巧出於你<br />\n垂頭前 沒緣分喪氣<br />\n睡到醒 才站立得起<br />\n盲目過 便看到天機<br />\n反覆往來 又再做回自己<br />\n<br />\n即時一生多出一根刺<br />\n沒有刺痛別要知<br />\n就當共你 有劇情沒有故事<br />\n<br />\n如煙 因給你遞過火<br />\n如火 卻也沒熔掉我<br />\n回望最初 當喪失是得著可不可<br />\n可痛若驪歌 樂如兒歌<br />\n像你沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<br />\n如花 超生了沒有果<br />\n如果 過路能重踏過<br />\n就當最初 是碎步湖上可不可<br />\n不種下甚麼 摘來甚麼<br />\n像我沒來過 沒去過"},{"pid":"b3250b9fc8ba0d6ab264683ca332633dffbeace8","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255d6fd80157db7de260896c30432b95e20988d2","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T10:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349d5fb7cbd4e552c1fb1cd584b5434fbd4ad164","tid":300980,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:00:44.000Z","msg":"呢首好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b010b9ea7e97e202d9c3363d0fcb0b684c30af35","tid":300980,"uid":63521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"皮已正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔熟嘅歌都係睇人點解好"},{"pid":"784c8576d3c082289364d9abc98d3f44ca08f3d1","tid":300980,"uid":63521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:03:33.000Z","msg":"樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332bf56491cc00208c95abf1d25a15a8fc4d8502","tid":300980,"uid":20524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"3989ce5eb3f88c9298cce3c196bca381687120d1","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢首好屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢首之前上過好多次高連登神枱"},{"pid":"77dab7b1deef41a503a31dd3f27cae8eadc39fb5","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來"},{"pid":"ac5a5fdf2db584cc6b36ec3acbcc41e9e59c652f","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ab367fa04521a81cdfdb2ce666ae5ab786ec82","tid":300980,"uid":73155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:31:50.000Z","msg":"借火都好正"},{"pid":"f5a41bce5b7a5a8c04e74b8244cbc7b4bc157e55","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借火都好正</blockquote><br />\n剛剛要去便利店裡為著香煙無人點火 正巧你真走所出路上...."},{"pid":"09da7d3c2e046805fbdb60fc8a8c0734b7ac453c","tid":300980,"uid":28792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"不來也不去其實無咩解，都係上善若水嘅概念<br />\n神係神在文字遊戲<br />\n<br />\n1.垂頭時個段係講緊垂字嘅變化<br />\n2.有舊情沒有往事 之段駁個如煙上去<br />\n3.煙字殘體係火因，就係因給你遞過火<br />\n3.如果 一語雙相"},{"pid":"c2b6fb474b4dd03c2ed2d258673901022cc881be","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不來也不去其實無咩解，都係上善若水嘅概念<br />\n神係神在文字遊戲<br />\n<br />\n1.垂頭時個段係講緊垂字嘅變化<br />\n2.有舊情沒有往事 之段駁個如煙上去<br />\n3.煙字殘體係火因，就係因給你遞過火<br />\n3.如果 一語雙相</blockquote><br />\n唔係講緊個concept就算<br />\n我相信樓主想做嘅係文本細讀<br />\n咁解法先有意義<br />\n<br />\nBtw樓豬我好撚鍾意呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831f91cbd1ba2a1323f13ed4f21205dc199cb4ee","tid":300980,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算"},{"pid":"a6985c8e0da4853b1ba635772b3afd45286c3293","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n屌白玫瑰我都好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得白玫瑰冇咩研究價值 太直白"},{"pid":"43317787b7add5121fb6957a8544cb77e81bcd72","tid":300980,"uid":39402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n屌白玫瑰我都好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得白玫瑰冇咩研究價值 太直白</blockquote><br />\n依首..迷過一排<br />\n好籠統咁去用一句作結論既話<br />\n得不到的 從來矜貴<br />\n<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"39ed51581676deef4b4932c3cde7f87ad1cb1a4d","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n屌白玫瑰我都好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得白玫瑰冇咩研究價值 太直白</blockquote><br />\n依首..迷過一排<br />\n好籠統咁去用一句作結論既話<br />\n得不到的 從來矜貴<br />\n<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n鍾意應該係因為有共嗚同埋音樂正<br />\n從賞析角度冇咩特別"},{"pid":"b263315030e93cc71ed26e29e209e9cdf0aaa913","tid":300980,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"推介鍾意廣東歌詞既人一本書<br />\n<br />\n叫夜話港樂"},{"pid":"54a530f64a9c61f76b04888f121da099b901fcbc","tid":300980,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:05:31.000Z","msg":"留名睇研究"},{"pid":"f4275bd2677337ac5f513722fb7f79223377bcfe","tid":300980,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n屌白玫瑰我都好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得白玫瑰冇咩研究價值 太直白</blockquote><br />\n依首..迷過一排<br />\n好籠統咁去用一句作結論既話<br />\n得不到的 從來矜貴<br />\n<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n鍾意應該係因為有共嗚同埋音樂正<br />\n從賞析角度冇咩特別</blockquote><br />\n講真 最正係mv個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47214c9c64957d6fa5ea6a0772263794939987a3","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n屌白玫瑰我都好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得白玫瑰冇咩研究價值 太直白</blockquote><br />\n依首..迷過一排<br />\n好籠統咁去用一句作結論既話<br />\n得不到的 從來矜貴<br />\n<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n有無聽過他一個人<br />\n好想知到底 個他係唔係我<br />\n想知他只係一個主角好寂莫既朋友 定係係以前經歷好寂莫既主角自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830a7a70cafdd785f6af255fd82ee017ce881177","tid":300980,"uid":2071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"和你對弈輸贏都回不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ababc27b9bf054fdfb7483ffb57ea685fb554d3a","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:07:26.000Z","msg":"由第一句揚帆配人潮已經絕到我扯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304a0ae13fac5fd03e210f66dd65b1a035e5ceff","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不來也不去其實無咩解，都係上善若水嘅概念<br />\n神係神在文字遊戲<br />\n<br />\n1.垂頭時個段係講緊垂字嘅變化<br />\n2.有舊情沒有往事 之段駁個如煙上去<br />\n3.煙字殘體係火因，就係因給你遞過火<br />\n3.如果 一語雙相</blockquote><br />\n唔係講緊個concept就算<br />\n我相信樓主想做嘅係文本細讀<br />\n咁解法先有意義<br />\n<br />\nBtw樓豬我好撚鍾意呢首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係想每字每句去咀嚼<br />\n成個concept相信唔少人明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cff36b7ac29f74f1437c8781438399a91509be4e","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n屌白玫瑰我都好鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我覺得白玫瑰冇咩研究價值 太直白</blockquote><br />\n依首..迷過一排<br />\n好籠統咁去用一句作結論既話<br />\n得不到的 從來矜貴<br />\n<br />\n講完</blockquote><br />\n鍾意應該係因為有共嗚同埋音樂正<br />\n從賞析角度冇咩特別</blockquote><br />\n講真 最正係mv個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHehe<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b8da0a1daec22741a4f280d413d28c9170ff8d","tid":300980,"uid":81012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote