未有嘅我</span><br />\n<br />\n即時一生多出一根刺<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">即使共你嘅回憶永遠無法忘記</span><br />\n沒有刺痛別要知<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇傷感就唔再理</span><br />\n就當共你 有劇情沒有故事<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">就當你我之間我段過去，但永遠唔會有結尾，一段冇結局嘅劇情，點稱得上故事</span><br />\n<br />\n如煙 因給你遞過火<br />\n如火 卻也沒熔掉我<br />\n回望最初 當喪失是得著可不可<br />\n可痛若驪歌 樂如兒歌<br />\n像你沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<br />\n如花 超生了沒有果<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我共你 就好似花超生左咁 唔會結到果</span><br />\n如果 過路能重踏過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我地一齊經歷過嘅 可以再走多一遍</span><br />\n就當最初 是碎步湖上可不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不如就當當初係湖上行 不留一點痕跡</span><br />\n不種下甚麼 摘來甚麼<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">冇播下種 冇結過果</span><br />\n像我沒來過 沒去過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我冇黎過冇去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n打錯左字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e2c89c9896d44914c139089c6dd75dd6a1fe3f1","tid":300980,"uid":93776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主一陣解唔解白玫瑰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首我都好撚鐘意 我都想大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但是無人來</blockquote><br />\n歌詞研究真係好小人做<br />\n自己斷斷續續研究左5 6年 每次同身邊人講 都係無乜反應<br />\n後來決定自己研究算</blockquote><br />\n睇開酒詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ad23dfce0d111a3de1e29968ee1045d912461d","tid":300980,"uid":93776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"學愛你　美不美　天黑黑到地<br />\n朝著壞了的燈泡舞著別離<br />\n其實地球沒有你　站到虛脫便會飛<br />\n何必怪責雙腳　未夠伶俐　不比你優美<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca1a4f1b86abbb75c64a3c17c0938b279cee653","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學愛你　美不美　天黑黑到地<br />\n朝著壞了的燈泡舞著別離<br />\n其實地球沒有你　站到虛脫便會飛<br />\n何必怪責雙腳　未夠伶俐　不比你優美<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 呢首我top 10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9430c79c86d580f288d717d3a17aa2b9fcbfe36","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學愛你　美不美　天黑黑到地<br />\n朝著壞了的燈泡舞著別離<br />\n其實地球沒有你　站到虛脫便會飛<br />\n何必怪責雙腳　未夠伶俐　不比你優美<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌 呢首我top 10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好悽美嘅詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤如自卑水銀瀉地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e415162630cf01e68357d90ace4baa64e8d32cc8","tid":300980,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"不如下首解黑暗中漫舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25b7d63c6960520695d340e5f516789a4580adc","tid":300980,"uid":93776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如下首解黑暗中漫舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n完全match春光乍洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b49c1f05064ff60e8a423574acc5c05f84e5e61","tid":300980,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T12:02:21.000Z","msg":"如烟，因給你遞過火<br />\n正過<br />\n愁莫渡江，秋心拆兩半<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b7352fe456509e85459f4844124ff2e6804a45","tid":300980,"uid":109050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:15:08.000Z","msg":"JUNO 好多歌都唔明,但歌詞好似好有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中最想知果首係 灰 , 聽左十萬次都唔明<br />\n有無人可以解讀下<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n墳場上派對　然後就散去<br />\n懷疑甚麼可叫你感觸到　讓眼淚流出變沙<br />\n靈魂在切割　然後被吃喝<br />\n懷疑甚麼使我安心走來　安心得使你想喊<br />\n<br />\n能隨時含著十架　再脫去遮羞的髮<br />\n還會還會為你穿灰色的婚紗<br />\n在偉大偉大城市　還會愛嗎<br />\n哪個跪下　要吻青蛙<br />\n<br />\n完成我蒼白　完成你暗黑　出生比死去更可怕<br />\n到底太多瘋人情願自殘　太多詩人需要被殺<br />\n如凡人　飛不高　至少沉下<br />\n<br />\n原來我的眉逐漸在蒼白　為著你眼中的暗黑<br />\n攜著烏鴉回家　迎著未來塌下　相信你　仍然會喊<br />\n<br />\n能隨時埋在垃圾　與世界一起風化<br />\n還會還會為你開灰色的櫻花<br />\n未拍下快樂快樂遺照　還會愛嗎<br />\n哪個跪下　要吻青蛙<br />\n<br />\n完成我蒼白　完成你暗黑　出生比死去更可怕<br />\n攜著烏鴉回家　迎著未來塌下　相信你　仍然會喊<br />\n<br />\n看著你眼淚　流下到一和零之間<br />\n還令我碎裂到變為兩堆沙<br />\n<br />\n完成我嗎　來完成我好嗎　出生比死去更可怕<br />\n到底太多光明無力奉還　太多幽靈誕下<br />\n如凡人　飛不高　至少沉下<br />\n<br />\n原來我的眉逐漸在蒼白　為著你眼中的暗黑<br />\n攜著烏鴉回家　迎著未來塌下　相信你　仍然會喊<br />\n<br />\n可否繼續　為我喊"},{"pid":"e0752a6dc84f92f265ca956a6d0092e3661aa89c","tid":300980,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T17:00:24.000Z","msg":"男人心一字馬"},{"pid":"2e1bbec7f6d93130ad8eae97bb8ea5aca965182a","tid":300980,"uid":16713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:16:22.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解下宋冬野？<br />\n鴿子"},{"pid":"f0af153b4de5571b3ced838cab8b94fa3edd9294","tid":300980,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"鐘意綿綿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30a56c9508574e4d7ebf16083b27d8f9df62e9e","tid":300980,"uid":7628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:18:39.000Z","msg":"周柏豪<br />\n還記得櫻花正開～"},{"pid":"45e023057bf689b03de9c819ee02221de6d053bd","tid":300980,"uid":103200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T16:21:26.000Z","msg":"一絲不掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}